These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid
1. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Flower   | zinnia | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, may
1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Birthday   | october | may |

 #################################

 
